# Feature model

Variables:
1. Vegetation index (google earth engine)
1. Night lights (google earth engine)
1. Number of pools (leaflets images)
1. Distance from the nearest pharmacy (public shapes repository)
1. Distance from the nearest subway station (public shapes repository)
1. Distance from the nearest supermarket (public shapes repository)
1. Distance from the nearest Police station (public shapes repository)
1. Distance from the nearest supermarket (google maps)


---

